hujadze}}\n* {{FootballDatabase.eu|74547}}\n* {{Soccerway|shalva-khujadze/325641}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Khujadze, Shalva}}\n[[Category:1975 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Footballers from Georgia (country)]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers from Georgia (country)]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Ukraine]]\n[[Category:Expatriates from Georgia (country) in Ukraine]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Greece]]\n[[Category:FC Nyva Ternopil players]]\n[[Category:FC Dinamo Tbilisi players]]\n[[Category:Georgia (country) international footballers]]\n[[Category:FC Dinamo Batumi players]]\n[[Category:Ukrainian Premier League players]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n\n\n{{Georgia-footy-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{use dmy dates|date=September 2011}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name= Shalva Khujadze\n| fullname = \n| image = \n| birth_date = {{birth date and age|df=yes|1975|10|5}} \n| birth_place = \n| height = {{height|m=1.80}}\n| currentclub = \n| clubnumber = \n| position = [[Midfielder]]\n| youthyears1= \n| youthclubs1= \n| years1 = 1992\u20131993 | years2 = 1993\u20131995 | years3 = 1995\u20131996 | years4 = 1997\u20131998 | years5 = 1998 | years6 = 1999 | years7 = 1999\u20132000 | years8 = 2000\u20132001 | years9 = 2001\u20132002 | years10 = 2002 | years11 = 2002 | years12 = 2003\u20132004 | years13 =2004\u20132005\n| clubs1 = [[Gorda Rustavi]] | clubs2 = [[FC Dinamo Tbilisi]] | clubs3 = [[FC Kolkheti-1913 Poti]] | clubs4 = [[FC Torpedo Kutaisi]] | clubs5 = [[FC Nyva Ternopil]] | clubs6 = [[FC Lokomotivi Tbilisi]] | clubs7 = [[FC Dinamo Batumi]] | clubs8 = [[Merani-91 Tbilisi]] | clubs9 = FC Dinamo Batumi | clubs10 = [[A.O. Agios Nikolaos Kritis]] | clubs11 = FC Dinamo Batumi | clubs12 = [[FC Sioni Bolnisi]] | clubs13 =FC Dinamo Batumi\n| caps1 = 20 | goals1 = 0 | caps2 = 23 | goals2 = 1 | caps3 = 34 | goals3 = 4 | caps4 = 43 | goals4 = 5 | caps5 = 6 | goals5 = 0 | caps6 = 13 | goals6 = 1 | caps7 = 19 | goals7 = 0 | caps8 