vid Austin\n* 2016 Vale of Clwyd: Dr John Kenyon\n* 2017 Ironbridge: [[Prys Morrgan|Prof Prys Morgan]]\n* 2018 Llandridod Wales: Dr Mark Redknap\n* 2019 Haverford West: Profesor Nancy Edwards                              \n{{colend}}\n\n==References==\n {{reflist}}\n\n==Bibliography==\n* {{cite book |first1=Nancy |last1=Edwards |first2=John |last2=Gould |chapter=From Antiquarians to Archaeologists in Nineteenth-Century Wales: The Question of Prehistory |editor1-first=N. |editor1-last=Evans |editor2-first=H. |editor2-last=Pryce |title=Writing a Small Nation's Past: Wales in Comparative Perspective 1850\u20131950 |place=Farnham |publisher=Ashgate |year=2013 |pages=143\u2013164 }}\n* {{cite journal |first=R. W. D. |last=Fenn |title=R. W. Banks and the Cambrian Archaeological Association |journal=Archaeologia Cambrensis |volume=154 |year=2005 |pages=1\u201316 }}\n* {{cite book |first=Evelyn |last=Lewes |title=Out with the Cambrians |place=London |publisher=Williams and Norgate |year=1934 }}\n* {{cite journal |first=H. Noel |last=Jarman |title=Contacts with the Cambrians for over Fifty Years |journal=Archaeologia Cambrensis |volume=131 |pages=1\u201317 }}\n* {{cite book |last1=Jenkins |first1=R. T. |authorlink1=Robert Thomas Jenkins |last2=Ramage |first2=Helen M. |year=1951 |title=A History of the Honourable Society of Cymmrodorion and of the Gwyneddigion and Cymreigyddion Societies (1751\u20131951) |place=London |publisher=Honourable Society of Cymmrodorion |series=Y Cymmrodor |volume=50 }}\n* {{cite book |first=Sir John Edward |last=Lloyd |author-link=John Edward Lloyd |chapter=Introduction: A History of the Cambrian Archaeological Association |editor-first=V. E. |editor-last=Nash-Williams |title=A Hundred Years of Welsh Archaeology: Centenary Volume 1846\u20131946 |publisher=Cambrian Archaeological Association |place=Gloucester |year=1946 }}\n* {{cite journal |first=Donald |last=Moore |title=Cambrian Meetings 1847\u20131997: A Society's Contribution in a Changing Arch